00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:04,480
Allocation on demand, right?

564
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,240
Exactly.

565
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,720
If it's really allocation on demand,

566
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,590
those few tents

567
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:09,350
aren't even enough for half
our asses to sit on.

568
00:30:09,350 --> 00:30:09,720
That's right.

569
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,110
Your ass must be really big.

570
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,240
We Southern Army

571
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,000
weren't raised by "concubines" either.

572
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,510
That's right.

573
00:30:13,510 --> 00:30:14,310
Whether born of the "legitimate wife"

574
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:15,710
or born of a "concubine,"

575
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:17,830
don't you know your place?

576
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,200
Watch your language!

577
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,320
How dare you speak like that!

578
00:30:22,350 --> 00:30:23,350
That's going too far!

579
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:24,070
Gentlemen!

580
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:29,240
The Chief Judge sent me here

581
00:30:29,510 --> 00:30:30,860
to only handle the allocation,

582
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:32,260
not to listen to demands.

583
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,350
So don't waste your time appealing to me

584
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:36,510
about how much you need them

585
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:38,930
or how difficult your situation is.

586
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:40,910
It's useless.

587
00:30:41,750 --> 00:30:43,350
The available field tents

588
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:44,940
are just this many.

589
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:48,350
In total,

590
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:50,240
there are 324 tents.

591
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:52,240
After deducting

592
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,590
the 54 tents needed by
the General Headquarters,

593
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:55,240
there are 270 left.

594
00:30:56,290 --> 00:30:59,090
The participating units consist of
two divisions

595
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,760
and two mixed brigades,

596
00:31:01,050 --> 00:31:03,580
totaling nine brigades with
over 33,000 men.

597
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,700
We'll allocate the tents by brigade,

598
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:09,460
which comes to exactly 30 tents
per brigade.

599
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,590
30 tents?

600
00:31:10,630 --> 00:31:11,260
30?

601
00:31:11,280 --> 00:31:12,960
Half of our men will be left out
in the sun.

602
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,200
That's not enough.

603
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:16,480
isn't this just pushing

604
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,350
the problem onto us?

605
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:18,830
Exactly.

606
00:31:21,110 --> 00:31:21,720
30 tents,

607
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:23,000
that's far too few.

608
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:23,720
Gentlemen.

609
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:24,960
Gentlemen!

610
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:27,010
This won't do. It's too few.

611
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,070
The headquarters

612
00:31:32,110 --> 00:31:33,440
has just been established.

613
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,240
We're poor.

614
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,110
These are all we have.

615
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:39,110
Each of you can only get this many.

616
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,600
If you can house a battalion,

617
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,050
then house a battalion.

618
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:44,510
If you can't house a battalion,

619
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,880
then house two companies.

620
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:47,590
If you can't even house two companies,

621
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:50,750
then distribute them to the companies
as company headquarters.

622
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,480
In any case,

623
00:31:51,830 --> 00:31:53,560
there's not a single tent more.

624
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:54,980
If you don't want them,

625
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:55,970
then forget it.

626
00:31:56,830 --> 00:31:58,350
What's that supposed to mean?

627
00:31:58,350 --> 00:31:59,350
What kind of talk is this?

628
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:00,350
If you really do this, we'll go home.

629
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:01,070
Fine, fine.

630
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:01,800
Let's just go home then.

631
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:03,400
Let me remind you all.

632
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,480
This time,

633
00:32:05,830 --> 00:32:07,440
everyone from the Empress Dowager

634
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:09,590
to the diplomats and reporters

635
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:11,300
from various countries stationed in China

636
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:13,430
are keeping a close watch on our drill.

637
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,510
Not to mention

638
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:16,590
whether there are enough tents
to go around.

639
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:18,450
Even if there were no tents at all,

640
00:32:19,220 --> 00:32:21,080
I don't believe any of you misters

641
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:23,590
would let this show

642
00:32:24,620 --> 00:32:25,780
fall apart.

643
00:32:36,010 --> 00:32:36,540
Alright.

644
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:38,640
30 tents it is.

645
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:39,930
It's better than nothing.

646
00:32:39,930 --> 00:32:40,650
I'll sign.

647
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:41,280
You...

648
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,590
This... This...

649
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,550
They signed so quickly.

650
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,690
Duke, hurry up and sign.

651
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:50,330
If you don't sign now,

652
00:32:50,330 --> 00:32:51,870
we won't even have 30 tents left.

653
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:52,880
Just sign it.

654
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:53,960
Alright, alright.

655
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:54,830
Let's go.

656
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:22,780
Who is this person?

657
00:33:23,350 --> 00:33:24,640
He's Yang Kaizhi.

658
00:33:25,170 --> 00:33:26,500
You don't even know him?

659
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:30,510
He used to be a classmate of
the Chief Judge.

660
00:33:31,410 --> 00:33:34,030
The one who settled things
with the Japanese in Yanji.

661
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:35,630
No wonder he's so efficient.

662
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,510
As they say,

663
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:40,700
the bolder you are, the greater
your skills must be.

664
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:48,240
[The Chief Judge Is the Up-and-Coming
Manchu General Liang Xiang]

665
00:33:58,110 --> 00:33:59,440
I'm heading to the bank.

