00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,460
That overseas donation transferred

667
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,810
from Tokyo has arrived.

668
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,840
How much should we withdraw?

669
00:34:06,670 --> 00:34:07,600
Withdraw it all.

670
00:34:08,179 --> 00:34:09,179
All?

671
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:09,719
Yes.

672
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,620
Convert it all to cash.

673
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:13,420
We'll need it for a bunch of stuff.

