00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:14,880
Converting so much cash at once,

675
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:15,949
wouldn't that be too conspicuous?

676
00:34:15,949 --> 00:34:17,550
Then withdraw it in batches.

677
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,480
Withdrawing small amounts in batches

678
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,840
might take some time.

679
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:24,400
At least 10 days.

680
00:34:24,429 --> 00:34:26,290
Will that be in time for our needs?

681
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,590
10 days.

682
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:30,030
Xu Xilin from Anqing

683
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:31,590
is in a bit of a hurry for the money.

684
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:32,230
However,

685
00:34:32,469 --> 00:34:33,510
Qiu Jin from Shaoxing

686
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,840
can wait a few more days.

687
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,489
Within 10 days it is, then.

688
00:34:38,690 --> 00:34:39,290
Oh, right.

689
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:40,360
Ask Wang Han

690
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,480
who came from Zhangde, Henan,

691
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,679
to come here to see me.

692
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:46,340
He's been waiting for me at the hotel
across the street.

693
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,880
Where's his mother?

694
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,610
She went off to run her errands.

695
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:13,960
Why did you put this thing

696
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:14,960
in the room?

697
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,550
It's novel, isn't it?

698
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:17,360
Your Yifan

699
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,800
has never cared for such things.

700
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,280
There's a kid in the room.

701
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:21,810
You should be more careful.

702
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:22,800
My son has grown up

703
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,510
with these things since he was born.

704
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:25,390
Come here.

705
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:36,800
Touch it.

706
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,800
Tianbai, what are you doing?

707
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,550
How can you let a kid

708
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,380
touch such a thing?

709
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:41,800
Don't worry, it's safe.

710
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:42,800
Come on.

711
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:44,400
Daddy will touch it with you.

712
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,030
In today's China,

713
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,440
there probably isn't anyone else

714
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,700
with my level of skill.

715
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:55,110
Alright, Son.

716
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:55,880
You've already transferred your luck

717
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,760
to it.

718
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:58,280
Come on. Give him to me.

719
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,550
Let's go find your mother, all right?

720
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,360
Let's go find your mother.

721
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,030
Mommy.

722
00:36:03,230 --> 00:36:04,280
Mommy. Hug me.

723
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,280
A little boy's urine can cure diseases.

724
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,280
Did you know that?

725
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:11,950
Look.

726
00:36:12,550 --> 00:36:13,590
No one likes you.

727
00:36:16,130 --> 00:36:17,050
Why don't you

728
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,190
go find that

729
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:22,030
rising noble?

730
00:36:24,690 --> 00:36:26,000
Maybe he'll like you.

731
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:29,360
Just stick on his waist

732
00:36:29,420 --> 00:36:31,420
and bloom into a beautiful flower.

733
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,630
Son.

734
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:48,260
[Autumn Military Drill Command Special]

735
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:52,840
Kaizhi.

736
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,800
I debuted earlier,

737
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:57,800
but your luck is certainly better.

738
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,960
It's not about luck.

739
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,960
I believe whether I'm used or
set aside is up to the times;

740
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:04,840
but whether I act or withdraw is up to me.

741
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:07,110
Kaizhi, this is not flattery, but

742
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:08,510
before the autumn military drill,

743
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:10,170
like raindrops pouring down,

744
00:37:10,230 --> 00:37:12,000
among the officers above the rank of
battalion commander,

745
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:14,400
about a dozen were promoted
out of nowhere.

746
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,240
All of them were Manchus,

747
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:18,410
and you were the only Han Chinese.

748
00:37:20,550 --> 00:37:21,320
Is that so?

749
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,320
Kaizhi,

750
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:27,000
you earned it with your military
achievements at the border.

751
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:28,190
We're all convinced.

752
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:28,800
Right?

753
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,840
But the rest of them,

754
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,670
they all got promoted through this.

755
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,360
Is that true?

756
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,230
Kaizhi, you stick to the Chief Judge

757
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:42,190
every day, inseparable,

758
00:37:42,190 --> 00:37:43,790
how do you not even know this?

759
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,000
Nowadays,

760
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:47,630
which rank doesn't have a price tag?

761
