It's all openly priced.

762
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:53,210
What kind of nonsense is this?

763
00:37:53,610 --> 00:37:54,470
Just like that,

764
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:57,320
Manchu generals are leading Han soldiers?

765
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,510
How come everyone leaves

766
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:21,570
as soon as I show up?

767
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,590
Right.

768
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,660
Why did they all leave?

769
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,420
It can't be helped.

770
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:28,210
You're the Chief Judge.

771
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,280
If it weren't because you're
the Chief Judge,

772
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,480
I would have left too.

773
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,480
Commander-in-Chief just

774
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:40,110
