775
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:41,360
I'm quite surprised.

776
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:42,770
What situation?

777
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,230
Do you know that

778
00:38:47,740 --> 00:38:49,180
the court originally planned

779
00:38:49,180 --> 00:38:50,280
