782
00:38:53,470 --> 00:38:54,950
How is this news?

783
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,480
This means

784
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,760
Empress Cixi is still

785
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:00,630
