794
00:39:25,570 --> 00:39:27,120
As long as the price is right,

795
00:39:27,120 --> 00:39:29,280
whether it's Manchu generals
or Han soldiers,

796
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:31,360
they all have to sit in line
and take their share.

797
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,470
That can't be.

798
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,800
He personally conveyed

799
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,200
the general policy to me.

800
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,190
As the Commander-in-Chief,

801
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:37,760
how could he go back on his word?

802
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:38,960
What general policy?

803
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:42,230
Anyway, it's aimed at Yuan Shikai.

804
00:39:42,230 --> 00:39:43,290
Isn't this absurd?

805
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:44,760
The blueprint of design

806
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,230
is based on the Japanese Army's

807
00:39:46,230 --> 00:39:47,230
Battle of Mukden,

808
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:48,360
but the target

809
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:49,840
is the former Commander-in-Chief

810
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:51,510
of the Beiyang Army.

811
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,450
Now that you put it that way,

812
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,240
I'm all confused.

813
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,050
