00:40:07,180 --> 00:40:08,780
What autumn military drill?

818
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:10,810
It was all just an act to begin with.

819
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:12,030
Look at you.

820
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:14,220
Why should you waste your energy?

