I didn't expect to find such a
fancy hotel here.

824
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:34,280
That's right.

825
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:34,970
You could say this place is like

826
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:36,290
half a hometown to

827
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:37,360
the Viceroy of Zhili.

828
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:39,840
Our hotel was personally funded by him
last year

829
00:40:39,840 --> 00:40:40,940
